# macOS
.DS_Store

# SKiDL ERC artifacts — `ERC()` writes <script>.erc and <script>.log
# into the current working directory. The prevention-benchmark
# reproducers under .plans/prevention-benchmark/skidl/ trigger these
# at the repo root when the user runs them; they're not source.
*.erc
*.log

# MkDocs build output — `mkdocs build` writes the static site here.
# Local-only; CI uploads it to GitHub Pages as an artifact instead.
/site/
